data.description: Great Central PB County Single Family Home, has 3 Br 2 Baths, 1783' Living Area has Ceramic tiling except bedrooms, Crown Molding & chair rail molding, Screened patio,Split Bedroom plan, 2 car garage that has Epoxy style painted floors. **Brand New Tile Roof in Dec 2023($43K). Quartz Kitchen Counters. It is Comfortable & Bright with plenty of light. River Bridge is a Gated Community that offers quiet, & peaceful living to enjoy your life in a convenient location that has amenities, such as Clubhouse with Fitness Center, 2 community Pools, Pickle ball, Playground, great walking paths/sidewalks and even shows!  Plus the HOA Fee is reasonable, & includes Lawn Care, Wifi, Cable w/ HBO, Starz etc, Gated, & amenities. Near, Polo, Equestrian, Airport, Beaches, fine dining, shopping & more
